lisim Award. Palfreman has written, directed and produced documentaries on a wide range of topics, but specializes in topical and often controversial issues involving science and medicine. Palfreman is the author of Brainstorms: The Race to Unlock the Mysteries of Parkinson's Disease, The Case of the Frozen Addicts: Working at the Edge of the Mysteries of the Human Brain (with J. William Langston), and The Dream Machine: Exploring the Computer Age (with Doron Swade). He is also president of the Palfreman Film Group.\n\n", "biography_author": "Wikidata", "date_of_biography": "2023-09-05T21:47:30.584021+10:00", "external_links": [{"id": 5936, "uri": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jon_Palfreman"}], "uuid": "9b5eca7d-4a8d-4498-8143-3e49a4b724e3", "source": {"name": "Vernon", "slug": "vernon"}, "source_identifier": "22617", "external_references": [{"id": 51892, "source": {"name": "Wikidata", "slug": "wikidata"}, "source_identifier": "Q20878193"}, {"id": 54922, "source": {"name": "VIAF", "slug": "viaf"}, "source_identifier": "166348218"}, {"id": 54923, "source": {"name": "LOC Auth", "slug": "loc-auth"}, "source_identifier": "n94803264"}], "date_modified": "2025-03-14T19:08:50.304259+11:00"}, {"id": 21518, "name": "Jane Nicholls", "roles_in_work": [{"id": 865180, "title": "Insearch of viewable objects", "work_id": 78740, "role": "director", "role_id": 938, "is_primary": true}, {"id": 2465107, "title": "Protect your back", "work_id": 85251, "role": "producer/director", "role_id": 31, "is_primary": true}], "also_known_as": "", "date_of_birth": "", "date_of_death": "", "genders": [], "languages": [], "places_of_operation": [], "biography": "", "biography_author": null, "date_of_biography": "2023-08-14T10:27:33.670407+10:00", "external_links": [], "uuid": "bff60791-ee13-45b1-bd27-71b756f42f30", "source": {"name": "Vernon", "slug": "vernon"}, "source_identifier": "21424", "external_references": [], "date_modified": "2023-08-14T10:27:33.670849+10:00"}, {"id": 21517, "name": "Mic